  const result = `## Deal Health: ${d.company_name} (${d.deal_id})

**Stage:** ${d.deal_stage || 'Unknown'} | **Salesforce:** ${d.salesforce_stage || 'N/A'}
**Scored:** ${scoredAt} | **Trend:** ${d.trend_direction || 'unknown'} (${(d.score_vs_previous || 0) >= 0 ? '+' : ''}${d.score_vs_previous || 0} pts)

### P2V2C2 Scores (${total}/30)
| Dimension | Score |
|---|---|
| Pain | ${d.pain_score || 0}/5 |
| Power | ${d.power_score || 0}/5 |
| Vision | ${d.vision_score || 0}/5 |
| Value | ${d.value_score || 0}/5 |
| Change | ${d.change_score || 0}/5 |
| Control | ${d.control_score || 0}/5 |

